title: Kanye West Thinks 'Keeping Up With the Kardashians' Should Win Emmys
text: Kanye West sits down for an interview on SHOWstudio on Tuesday (October 6). The 38-year-old rapper gave an in-depth two-hour interview in which he said his wife Kim Kardashian‘s reality show Keeping Up with the Kardashians should have won Emmys by now. “I feel proud to be in a family that has, you know, so [...] »
